name: Greedo (V)
Lore: 'Male Rodian bounty hunter. Sent by Jabba to capture Han. Arrogant, overconfident and not too bright. Trained by bounty hunters Nataz and Goa, who betrayed him to Thuku.',
Text: 'During battle, may cancel the game text of a smuggler present with Greedo for remainder of turn. During your control phase, may take one Oo-ta Goo-ta, Solo? into hand from Reserve Deck; reshuffle.',
